# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Software Project Types (swproj):
#   0 : MemoryTest - Calls basic  memorytest routines from common driver dir
#   1 : PeripheralTest - Calls any existing polled_example and/or selftest
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

